## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="1e02d-159">En el ejemplo de código siguiente se restablece la transformación geométrica de `pgBrush` a la identidad.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e02d-159">The following code example resets the geometric transform of `pgBrush` to identity.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="1e02d-160">Se supone que `myPath` ya es <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="1e02d-160">It is assumed that `myPath` is an existing <xref:System.Drawing.Drawing2D.GraphicsPath>.</span></span>  
  
